  "text": "In this fourth section, we first briefly summarize a popular approach to compute a detection map from the processed frame, i.e., the SNR t map [CITATION_1] , and list the shortcomings of this method. We then propose our novel detection map, the STIM map, and provide statistical guarantees for its subsequent thresholding based on our theoretical analysis.",
